          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>RevitalEyes is the world's most advanced at-home under-eye light therapy device, combining <strong>4 clinically proven modalities</strong> in one elegant device:</p><p><strong>• 660nm Red Light</strong> — Stimulates collagen production<br><strong>• 590nm Amber Light</strong> — Reduces dark circles &amp; puffiness<br><strong>• Low-Level Laser</strong> — Deep cellular rejuvenation<br><strong>• Microcurrent EMS</strong> — Lifts and tightens skin</p><p>Using the same technology trusted by dermatologists and aesthetic clinics worldwide — now available for home use.</p>"
          },
